    parentNode = scriptTag.parentNode;

e.innerHTML = "  <article style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">\n    <div style=\"margin-left: 0px;\">\n      <span class=\"t-article-body\">\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://www.moneyhelper.org.uk/en/everyday-money/credit-and-purchases/do-you-need-to-borrow-money\">\n<p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.moneyhelper.org.uk?utm_campaign=webfeeds\"><img src=\"https://www.moneyhelper.org.uk/etc.clientlibs/maps/core/clientlibs/clientlib-base/resources/logos/logo-en-desktop.svg\" alt=\"MoneyHelper\" /><\/a><\/p>\n<div class=\"aem-Grid aem-Grid--8 aem-Grid--default--8 \">        \n  <div class=\"title aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">\n    <div class=\"cmp-title-wrapper\">    \n      <div class=\"cmp-title cmp-title--h2\" id=\"deciding-whether-you-should-be-borrowing-money\">        \n        <h2 class=\"cmp-title__text h2-page-title\" tabindex=\"0\">            <span class=\"cmp-title__\"><\/span>                            Deciding whether you should be borrowing money                    <\/h2>\n            <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n  <div class=\"experiencefragment aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">        <\/div>\n  <div class=\"text aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">\n    <div class=\"cmp-text algolia-search-item  \">    \n      <p>There are some important questions you need to consider before you borrow money.<\/p>\n      <p>Ask yourself:<\/p>\n      <ul>\n        <li>Do I need to spend the money?<\/li>\n        <li>Are there any other ways of finding the money I need?<\/li>\n        <li>Can I afford to pay back the money I’m planning to borrow?<\/li>\n      <\/ul>\n          <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n  <div class=\"title aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">\n    <div class=\"cmp-title-wrapper\">    \n      <div class=\"cmp-title cmp-title--h3\" id=\"do-you-really-need-to-spend-the-money-at-all\">        \n        <h3 class=\"cmp-title__text h3-page-title\" tabindex=\"0\">            <span class=\"cmp-title__\"><\/span>                            Do you really need to spend the money at all?                    <\/h3>\n            <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n  <div class=\"text aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">\n    <div class=\"cmp-text algolia-search-item  \">    \n      <p>Before you borrow money, always make sure you actually need to borrow it.<br />\n        Are you struggling financially? Then it’s important to first make sure you’re claiming all the welfare benefits you’re entitled to and find out if you might be able to apply for support such as grants or rebates.<\/p>\n          <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n  <div class=\"calloutbox image aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">                                            \n    <h6>Find out more in our guide <a href=\"https://www.moneyhelper.org.uk/en/money-troubles/dealing-with-debt/make-sure-youre-getting-the-right-entitlements\" target=\"_self\" data-link-type=\"default\">Make sure you’re getting the right entitlements<\/a><\/h6>\n                                        <\/div>\n                  <!-- branch with multi links -->                                <!-- dominant callout image for mobile -->                                            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<div class=\"text aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">\n  <div class=\"cmp-text algolia-search-item  \">    \n    <p>Also see if there are other ways to cut back on your costs – for example, by switching energy, phone or internet provider.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n<div class=\"calloutbox image aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">                                            \n  <h6>Learn more about how to cut back on your day-to-day spending in our guide <a href=\"https://www.moneyhelper.org.uk/en/everyday-money/budgeting/how-to-save-money-on-household-bills\" target=\"_self\" data-link-type=\"default\">How to save money on household bills<\/a><\/h6>\n                                      <\/div>\n                <!-- branch with multi links -->                                <!-- dominant callout image for mobile -->                                            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<div class=\"text aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">\n  <div class=\"cmp-text algolia-search-item  \">    \n    <p>If you tend to buy things on impulse, try giving yourself a cooling off period of at least two days. When you’ve had a chance to think about it, you might find you’re not so keen to buy the item you wanted.<\/p>\n    <p>Try asking yourself:<\/p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Could I wait until I can afford to buy the item without borrowing?<\/li>\n      <li>Is there another way of getting it – for example, switching to a cheaper item, buying it second-hand or getting it for free from a recycling website?<\/li>\n    <\/ul>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n<div class=\"experiencefragment aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">        <\/div>\n<div class=\"title aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">\n  <div class=\"cmp-title-wrapper\">    \n    <div class=\"cmp-title cmp-title--h3\" id=\"can-you-save-up-or-use-savings-instead-of-borrowing-money\">        \n      <h3 class=\"cmp-title__text h3-page-title\" tabindex=\"0\">            <span class=\"cmp-title__\"><\/span>                            Can you save up or use savings instead of borrowing money?                    <\/h3>\n          <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n<div class=\"text aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">\n  <div class=\"cmp-text algolia-search-item  \">    \n    <p>If you don’t need the item today, it’s worth considering saving some money each month rather than taking out a loan.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n<div class=\"calloutbox image aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">                                            \n  <h3><b>Contact us<\/b><\/h3>\n                                      <\/div>\n                <!-- branch with multi links -->                                <!-- dominant callout image for mobile -->                                \n<div class=\"cmp-call-out-box__content-main-text\">                    <!-- Description -->                    \n  <div class=\"cmp-call-out-box__content-main-text-description\">                        \n    <p>We can help work out what’s right for you. Whatever your query we’re here to help. If we don’t know the answer, we’ll point you in the right direction of someone who does.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <!-- Bottom Text -->                    \n  <div class=\"cmp-call-out-box__content-main-text-link\">                        \n    <p>Find out how we can help on our <a data-link-type=\"default\" href=\"https://www.moneyhelper.org.uk/en/contact-us\" target=\"_self\">Contact us<\/a> page. <\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <!-- Button -->                                    <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<div class=\"title aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">\n  <div class=\"cmp-title-wrapper\">    \n    <div class=\"cmp-title cmp-title--h4\" id=\"saving-before-you-spend\">        \n      <h4 class=\"cmp-title__text h4-page-title\" tabindex=\"0\">            <span class=\"cmp-title__\"><\/span>                            Saving before you spend                    <\/h4>\n          <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n<div class=\"text aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">\n  <div class=\"cmp-text algolia-search-item  \">    \n    <p>If you can wait and save up for a purchase instead of using credit, it will cost you far less as you won’t have to pay any interest.<\/p>\n    <p>For example, if you wanted to buy something costing £600:<\/p>\n    <p>If you don’t have any savings, but can save, for example, £50 a month, it would take you a year to save the £600 and you would have earned interest on top of this.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n<div class=\"title aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">\n  <div class=\"cmp-title-wrapper\">    \n    <div class=\"cmp-title cmp-title--h4\" id=\"Cashing-in-savings\">        \n      <h4 class=\"cmp-title__text h4-page-title\" tabindex=\"0\">            <span class=\"cmp-title__\"><\/span>                            Cashing in savings                    <\/h4>\n          <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n<div class=\"text aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">\n  <div class=\"cmp-text algolia-search-item  \">    \n    <p>You will of course lose future potential interest on your savings if you use them up entirely for your purchase.<\/p>\n    <p>But this will still be much less than the interest you will have to pay if you borrow the money for the purchase, eg, on a credit card.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n<div class=\"back-to-top aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">\n  <div class=\"cmp-back-to-top\">    <a class=\"cmp-back-to-top__link\" href=\"#top\">        <span class=\"cmp-back-to-top__link-text\">Back to top<\/span>        <span class=\"cmp-back-to-top__link-icon\"><\/span>    <\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"title aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">\n  <div class=\"cmp-title-wrapper\">    \n    <div class=\"cmp-title cmp-title--h2\" id=\"if-you-do-decide-you-want-to-borrow-money\">        \n      <h2 class=\"cmp-title__text h2-page-title\" tabindex=\"0\">            <span class=\"cmp-title__\"><\/span>                            If you do decide you want to borrow money                    <\/h2>\n          <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n<div class=\"text aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">\n  <div class=\"cmp-text algolia-search-item  \">    \n    <p>If you definitely want, or need to borrow money, there are some important factors to consider.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n<div class=\"title aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">\n  <div class=\"cmp-title-wrapper\">    \n    <div class=\"cmp-title cmp-title--h3\" id=\"how-much-can-you-afford-to-repay\">        \n      <h3 class=\"cmp-title__text h3-page-title\" tabindex=\"0\">            <span class=\"cmp-title__\"><\/span>                            How much can you afford to repay?                    <\/h3>\n          <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n<div class=\"text aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">\n  <div class=\"cmp-text algolia-search-item  \">    \n    <p>It’s important to work out how much you can afford to repay each month, as this will affect which borrowing option is best for you.<\/p>\n    <p>Make sure you’re realistic about how much you could pay if, for example, your mortgage or rent went up, you had to spend more on things like energy bills, or your pay was cut.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n<div class=\"calloutbox image aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">                                            \n  <h6>Read our guide on <a href=\"https://www.moneyhelper.org.uk/en/everyday-money/credit-and-purchases/working-out-a-repayment-plan-for-your-borrowing\" target=\"_self\" data-link-type=\"default\">Working out a repayment plan for money you are borrowing<\/a><\/h6>\n                                      <\/div>\n                <!-- branch with multi links -->                                <!-- dominant callout image for mobile -->                                            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<div class=\"title aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">\n  <div class=\"cmp-title-wrapper\">    \n    <div class=\"cmp-title cmp-title--h3\" id=\"choosing-the-right-type-of-credit\">        \n      <h3 class=\"cmp-title__text h3-page-title\" tabindex=\"0\">            <span class=\"cmp-title__\"><\/span>                            Choosing the right type of credit                    <\/h3>\n          <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n<div class=\"text aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">\n  <div class=\"cmp-text algolia-search-item  \">    \n    <p>Also make sure you choose the right type of credit or loan for your situation.<\/p>\n    <p>Otherwise, you could find yourself paying more than you need to.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n<div class=\"calloutbox image aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">                                            \n  <h6>Read our guide on <a href=\"https://www.moneyhelper.org.uk/en/everyday-money/credit-and-purchases/deciding-on-the-best-type-of-credit-for-you\" target=\"_self\" data-link-type=\"default\">Deciding on the best type of credit for you<\/a><\/h6>\n                                      <\/div>\n                <!-- branch with multi links -->                                <!-- dominant callout image for mobile -->                                            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<div class=\"text aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">\n  <div class=\"cmp-text algolia-search-item  \">    \n    <p>When you’ve worked out what type of credit suits your situation, shop around and compare deals. It’s important to look at:<\/p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>the interest rate and the annual percentage rate (APR)<\/li>\n      <li>how much you’ll repay in total (in the case of loans)<\/li>\n      <li>any penalties for missed or late payments<\/li>\n      <li>the cost per week or month, and whether this might vary.<\/li>\n    <\/ul>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n<div class=\"calloutbox image aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">                                            \n  <h6>Find out more in our guide <a href=\"https://www.moneyhelper.org.uk/en/savings/how-to-save/interest-rates-explained\" target=\"_self\" data-link-type=\"default\">Interest rates explained<\/a><\/h6>\n                                      <\/div>\n                <!-- branch with multi links -->                                <!-- dominant callout image for mobile -->                                            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<div class=\"text aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">\n  <div class=\"cmp-text algolia-search-item  \">    \n    <p>If you have a poor credit rating, you might be tempted to use a home credit or a payday loan company, especially if you have few credit options.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n<div class=\"experiencefragment aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">    \n  <div class=\"cmp-experiencefragment cmp-experiencefragment--beware-of-loan-sharks\">\n    <div class=\"xf-content-height\">    \n      <div class=\"aem-Grid aem-Grid--12 aem-Grid--default--12 \">        \n        <div class=\"responsivegrid aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--12\">\n          <div class=\"aem-Grid aem-Grid--12 aem-Grid--default--12 \">        \n            <div class=\"calloutbox image aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--12\">                                            \n              <h3>Beware of loan sharks<\/h3>\n                                                  <\/div>\n                            <!-- branch with multi links -->                                <!-- dominant callout image for mobile -->                                \n            <div class=\"cmp-call-out-box__content-main-text\">                    <!-- Description -->                    \n              <div class=\"cmp-call-out-box__content-main-text-description\">                        \n                <p>Loan sharks often use online channels like social media to try and lend to people. This kind of lending is illegal and it could cost you a lot more than you think. <\/p>\n                                    <\/div>\n                                  <!-- Bottom Text -->                    \n              <div class=\"cmp-call-out-box__content-main-text-link\">                        \n                <p>Find out more about <a data-link-type=\"default\" href=\"https://www.moneyhelper.org.uk/en/money-troubles/dealing-with-debt/how-to-spot-a-loan-shark\" target=\"_self\">loan sharks and how to spot them<\/a><\/p>\n                                    <\/div>\n                                  <!-- Button -->                                    <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                  <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<div class=\"text aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">\n  <div class=\"cmp-text algolia-search-item  \">    \n    <p>Before signing up for a payday loan or any other type of high-cost borrowing. make sure you’ve explored all possible alternatives.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n<div class=\"calloutbox image aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">                                            \n  <h6>Find out more in our guides:<\/h6>\n  <h6><a data-link-type=\"default\" href=\"https://www.moneyhelper.org.uk/en/everyday-money/types-of-credit/payday-loans-other-ways-to-borrow\">Payday loans – other ways to borrow<\/a><\/h6>\n  <h6><a href=\"https://www.moneyhelper.org.uk/en/everyday-money/types-of-credit/home-credit-or-doorstep-lending\" target=\"_self\" data-link-type=\"default\">Home credit or doorstep lending<\/a><\/h6>\n                                      <\/div>\n                <!-- branch with multi links -->                                <!-- dominant callout image for mobile -->                                            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<div class=\"back-to-top aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--8\">\n  <div class=\"cmp-back-to-top\">    <a class=\"cmp-back-to-top__link\" href=\"#top\">        <span class=\"cmp-back-to-top__link-text\">Back to top<\/span>        <span class=\"cmp-back-to-top__link-icon\"><\/span>    <\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <!-- Informizely Voting Survey for \"moneyhelper.org.uk\" -->    \n<div class=\"cmp-voting__container cmp-voting__vote hide\">        \n  <div class=\"cmp-voting__informizely-form en hide\" id=\'informizely-embed-ziircnj\'>        <\/div>\n              <\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<p>This article is provided by the <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.moneyhelper.org.uk?utm_campaign=webfeeds\">MoneyHelper<\/a>.<\/p>\n<img src=\"//webfeeds.moneyadviceservice.org.uk/tracking/pixel.gif?feed_id=2009&feed_name=Borrowing&partner_id=176&partner_name=GroceryAid&source_item_id=12866&source_item_title=Do+you+need+to+borrow+money%3F+%7C+MoneyHelper&source_item_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneyhelper.org.uk%2Fen%2Feveryday-money%2Fcredit-and-purchases%2Fdo-you-need-to-borrow-money\" style=\"position:absolute; visibility:hidden\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />\n<\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/article>\n";
